{"lemma":"مُضْطَرِب","slug":"مُضْطَرِب","root":"ض.ر.ب","root_slug":"ض-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25720","n25721"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B6%D9%92%D8%B7%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%A8"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"agitated; disturbed; confounded; distraught; tumultuous"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of اِضْطَرَبَ (iḍṭaraba)."},"ipa":["/mudˤ.tˤa.rib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25720","headword_ar":"مُضْطَرَبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"may mean"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiDoTaraAbN","text_ar":"اِضْطَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. it may be used as an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiDoTaraba","text_ar":"اِضْطَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.), agreeably with a general rule]: ―         -b2-  and it may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiDoTiraAb","text_ar":"اِضْطِرَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ham p. 142:) [thus used it often means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which one goes to and fro seeking the means of subsistence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and simply"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which one seeks gain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiDoTaraba fiY","text_ar":"اِضْطَرَبَ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^umuwrihi","text_ar":"اُمُورِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also the syns."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muraAgamN","text_ar":"مُرَاغَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in two places) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munotafadN","text_ar":"مُنْتَفَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  [It is also a pass. part. n.: and hence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDoTarabaAtN lilomaEaA$i","text_ar":"مُضْطَرَبَاتٌ لِلْمَعَاشِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The things that are desired to be gained for subsistence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sustenance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAgibu","text_ar":"مَرَاغِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n25721","headword_ar":"مُضْطَرِبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[A thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having its several parts in a state of collision:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence, a thing, and a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of commotion, agitation, convulsion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see its verb, 8]. ―         -b2-  One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a muDoTariba","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ مُضْطَرِبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEinaAni","text_ar":"العِنَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came with quivering rein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he came discomfited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put to flight, and alone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN muDoTaribu Alxaloqi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ مُضْطَرِبُ الخَلْقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man incongruous, unsound, faulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak, in respect of make:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tall, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loose, lax, flabby, uncompact, slack, shaky,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not strong of make."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiyvN muDoTaribu Als~anadi","text_ar":"حَدِيثٌ مُضْطَرِبُ السَّنَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tradition unsound, faulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak, in respect of the authority upon which it rests,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to which it is traced up"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ascribed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxotal~N","text_ar":"مُخْتَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","TA"]}]}}